<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="container">
      <div id="banner">Coding School Alumni Association</div>
      <div id="content">
        <h1>Welcome, <%= @user.fname %>!</h1>
        <h2 class="subheading">
          You're now signed up for the Coding School Alumni Association.
        </h2>
        <hr>
        <div id="text">
          <p class="event">
            Our last event, a talk about scaling early startups, was on 2/18 at New Relic in San Francisco and  <a href="http://slid.es/jeremyruppel/hi-jeremy-what-do-you-know-about-startups">Jeremy's slides are available at slid.es</a>.
          </p>
          <p>  
            We've got the power of a large group of amazing people behind us and can use it to pull together some pretty exciting stuff: speakers, happy hours, education, hackathons, kickball teams... you name it, you got it. 
          </p>
          <p>
            So if you've got ideas or would like to get involved and help organize or contribute in any way, please let me know at <a href="mailto:erik@theodinproject.com">erik@theodinproject.com</a>.  We're also working to build a simple but useful alumni portal to replace the signup page you used to get this far.  It's an agile open-source project that could be great experience for you so please reach out if you'd like to help out.
          </p>
          <p>
            I can't wait to see you out at our next event!
          </p>
          <p>
            Sincerely,
          </p>
          <p class="signature">
            Erik Trautman <br>
            President, CSAA
          </p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <p class="about">
          The CSAA is a social and professional network of alumni from fulltime intensive coding schools that is dedicated to helping its members connect with each other and accelerate their careers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

